@page "/"

<div class="container custom-background-color">
     <div class="row">
         <div class="col-7 text-center my-auto">
             <span>Realtime Notifications Sent Straight to You</span>
             <h1>NotiFi</h1>
         </div>
        <div class="col-5 text-center">
          <img src="/Computer_Maya-Maceka.jpg" class="img-fluid" id="round_image" alt="Accessing online service with a laptop." />
        </div>
     </div>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div>
            <h2>Online Notification App</h2>
            <span>
                Keep track of your transactions with the Commerce Bank Notification Application. This online web application will provide
                options for you to:
            </span>
            <ul>
                <li>Set custom notifications for any type of transaction.</li>
                <li>Any notifications that have been triggered will prompt a message to be sent directly to your registered email address.</li>
                <li>View a summary on how many notifications have been triggered.</li>
                <li>View a detailed list of all transactions associated with your triggered notifications.</li>
                <li>View all your transactions for the current date.</li>
            </ul>
            <hr class="solid mt-5 custom_hr_solid" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-5 text-center">
            <img src="/Free_Image_Burst.jpg" class="img-fluid" id="square_Image" alt="Getting Started with Notification Web Application (Laptop)." />
        </div>
        <div class="col-7 text-center my-auto">
            <h2>Get started with the Online Notification App today!</h2>
            <h5>Set custom notifications to alert you of any kind of transactions.</h5>
            <span>
                Register for an online account through your local Commerce Bank branch. Once you have registered, you can log into the Online
                Notification Application immediately to set up notifications.
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="solid mt-5 custom_hr_solid" />
</div>